CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 11, 1974, pg. 11, reads: "At NAACP Dinner - Just before he addressed a sell-out crowd attending the 20th annual Human Rights Dinner at the Hilton Hotel last Thursday. Federal Communications Commissioner Benjamin Hooks talked with the chairman of the dinner, Mrs. Homer S. Brown. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Benjamin Hooks and Wilhelmina Byrd Brown posed in Hilton Hotel for 20th annual Human Rights Dinner
